xccm_hw.h File Reference

Detailed Description

This header file contains identifiers and register-level driver functions (or macros) that can be used to access the Xilinx Color Correction Matrix (CCM) core.

 MODIFICATION HISTORY:

 Ver   Who     Date     Changes
 ----- ------- -------- -------------------------------------------------------
 6.0   adk     03/06/14 First release.
                        Added the register offsets and bit masks for the
                        registers.
                        Added backward compatibility macros.
